overview: Welcome to our first official MADE IN CHELSEA Fitness Workout, MIC:FIT! We share the hottest fitness trends, that help us stay in shape when we’re not partying in Chelsea. These workouts will get you fit for St.Tropez and looking hot for The King’s Road! Get up close and personal with an exclusive look behind the scenes and transform your body with four dynamic 20 minute workouts, that could have only been Made in Chelsea. Let’s Do It!
title: Made in Chelsea - MIC: FIT
